# Visualization Quality Gate

## CHECKLIST (ALL MUST PASS)

1. Is there ONE clear insight?
2. Is chart understandable in <3 seconds?
3. Are all labels present?
4. Is scale honest and not misleading?
5. Are colors meaningful (not decorative)?
6. Is chart type correct?
7. Is anything unnecessary present?

## FAIL CONDITIONS

- missing title or labels
- wrong chart type
- cluttered layout
- misleading axis

## OUTPUT RULE

If any check fails → revise visualization BEFORE returning result